    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>A spectral guardian materializes, indistinct except for a gleaming sword and shield emblazoned with the symbol of your deity.</em></p><p><strong>Summoning Spell</strong> </p><ul><li><p>You summon a large celestial called a @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-summoned-creatures.Actor.aCyCujCraRmdGf2e]{Guardian of Faith}. It is immune to damage, all conditions, and cannot be targeted.</p></li><li><p><strong>Hazard:</strong> Any creature hostile to you rolls a dexterity save when they enter or when they end their turn within 10 ft. of the Guardian (but only once per turn).</p></li></ul><p><strong>Dexterity Saving Throw</strong> </p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> The creature takes [[/damage 20 radiant]] damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> The creature takes [[/damage 10 radiant]] damage.</p></li></ul><p>The spell ends and the guardian vanishes once it has dealt a total of 60 damage or more.</p>",
            "chat": "<strong>Summoning Spell</strong> </p><ul><li><p>You summon a large celestial called a @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-summoned-creatures.Actor.aCyCujCraRmdGf2e]{Guardian of Faith}. It is immune to damage, all conditions, and cannot be targeted.</p></li><li><p><strong>Hazard:</strong> Any creature hostile to you rolls a dexterity save when they enter or when they end their turn within 10 ft. of the Guardian (but only once per turn).</p></li></ul><p><strong>Dexterity Saving Throw</strong> </p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> The creature takes [[/damage 20 radiant]] damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> The creature takes [[/damage 10 radiant]] damage.</p></li></ul><p>The spell ends and the guardian vanishes once it has dealt a total of 60 damage or more.</p>"
        },
